                    "description": "I have a broad range of experience in both print and broadcast media commentary.  As well as appearing in numerous English-language publications, my articles have been translated into Vietnamese, Greek, Turkish, French, Spanish, Albanian, and Portuguese.\n\nMy articles on international affairs and U.S. foreign policy have appeared in either the print or online editions of Foreign Affairs, The National Interest, The Los Angeles Times, Stars and Stripes, The Boston Globe, The Guardian, The Daily Telegraph, The New Statesman, Gulf News (Dubai), Mail & Guardian (Johannesburg), The Huffington Post UK, The Diplomat, The Africa Times, The Scranton Times Tribune, (Pennsylvania), The Intelligencer (Pennsylvania), The Wapakoneta Daily News (Ohio), The Press of Atlantic City (New Jersey), The St. Paul Pioneer Press (Minnesota), The Milwaukee Independent and in a host of specialist foreign policy publications.\n\nI have also appeared on various broadcast media outlets including Australia's Radio National, SiriusXM, TRT World, LBC Radio, eNCA TV and others. I have acted as an expert source for outlets including The Atlantic, Al-Jazeera, The Globe & Mail, and more.",
